Plus, they have IPX4-rated protection from water and a 2-year extended warranty against dust and water. . Get up to 5.5 hours of Elite 85t battery life on a single charge with ANC on, with a total charge of up to 25 hours in the compact charging case. Plus, the powerful magnetic case snaps these earbud headphones firmly in place for maximum security. . Your Elite 85t earbuds will sound great as soon as you unbox them but downloading the Sound+ app will make them even better, with MySound & MyControls, call settings, customizable equalizer options for personalization and more.
